{"tid":273820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"信用卡提款密碼無效    AC米蘭迷怒毀便利店終端機","createTime":"2017-06-07T01:04:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-07T10:50:22.000Z","uid":48093,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1d667f31cf07b583c48160bfbf662678bedee50a","tid":273820,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T01:04:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170607/large/1496781044_f2ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170607%2Flarge%2F1496781044_f2ba.jpg&h=73ef6df0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n銅鑼灣邊寧頓街17號，凌晨2時許，3男1女進入一間便利店，其中一名醉酒男子取出信用卡，準備經便利店的終端機多次提取現金(註:一般提取每次上限500元)，惟當準備進行第二次取款時，男子多次輸入密碼均告無效，一怒將手上的終端機擲落地上，終端機撞擊損毀螢幕出現裂痕，職員於是報警，警員到場調查，列刑事毀壞案件處理，將其拘捕帶署調查。"},{"pid":"26e4b5938cd0edb786598cc78c705e358d742c27","tid":273820,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T01:05:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"43caa51d87f1a9eed008b1e8504e07fb91bea5e9","tid":273820,"uid":759,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T01:07:25.000Z","msg":"迪清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33aa4171d67e39e0654c5cdb58f37a980815a7a7","tid":273820,"uid":464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T01:10:51.000Z","msg":"{-;-}"},{"pid":"e52476ce6ff9f6d892cc33cf69e018b55fb40b77","tid":273820,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T01:16:27.000Z","msg":"家燕媽媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16656fe4eba470e76d6cf31014650306980fcf18","tid":273820,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T01:29:53.000Z","msg":"影衰晒"},{"pid":"0d1942920ede3e176227e6252dd09a7e507cdec2","tid":273820,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T01:30:53.000Z","msg":"咁暴力架乜"},{"pid":"bfb4ccb51f5